Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束 胜者八广 2：0
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs23}game set and match 来自草地网球用语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了兰前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用我的毛巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先都排成一列吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天按照AIUEO顺序
