Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}关于强化集训

Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这次的一年级成员怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有精神  很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 七惠你也稍微阻止一下她们啊  每次都那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被后辈们喜欢的帅气的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真薄情寡义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告诉你一个好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去交个男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七惠你坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我忍不住想欺负你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  和父亲两人生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但住这一整幢屋子是不是太大了点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不是很令人在意吗  这么厚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个里面满满的写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规定是不可以告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小气  文伽你真是什么都保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是福音局定下的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  上次那个男生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屋顶上追过来的那个戴着眼镜的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你还是人类的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊  美川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要向你父亲开枪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什么原因的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从那以后 一直都在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0913
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0913
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  呐  那个男生是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很拚命的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是文伽的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我们不都是合同认证过的关系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得搭档应该是相互信赖的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送信人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个是死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从死后的世界寄来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以称为死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后的 世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立石尚子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是寄信人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这也是理所应当的反应啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说  那算什么啊  真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是死了的话  才不帮你送死后文呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朝  给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的脸  发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长  兰前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来一起玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩纸牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我收敛点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会影响到其他的客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又有什么关系呢  队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是兰前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真通情达理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过相对的 输掉的人要场地快跑10个来回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:06:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么办文伽  他们都出了海鸥市了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 申请出差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 好久没去管辖区外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去外边咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡很讨厌这个城市么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是再喜欢的食物 每天都吃的话也会厌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公  你这么慢吞吞的没关系么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察不忙说明社会安定嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到美川了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前那起事件的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 七惠今年晋升到队长了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要的都写在这上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  5点左右送过来可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个我要去仓库看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  多买点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事叫的这么性感干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟男生交往的女人很恶心么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是讨厌男生呢  兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是和爸爸一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不算异性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶作剧的话是不是太缠人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这不是恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是立石尚子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃我的不是她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我没有接受的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有送到的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我是不会收的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  完全被讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这是死人发出来的信 都会让人感到害怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这封死后文能送到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真想得开啊  年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是千秋 为什么你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都出差到这里了 真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0923
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵子刚在上面见过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  这里是千秋的投递范围
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  我说……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认投递范围是搭档的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健忘这点倒很像个人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  你个番茄汁 给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是番茄  是真苫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你这张破嘴巴该换一张了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  你们的相声可以停了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面确实经常见到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地上是好久不见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以是  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强词夺理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  强词夺理强词夺理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文的投递人是死人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说年龄本应不会增长的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却不同  年龄在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次见你  你都长大了些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人

Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  全垒打 总共三个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事么  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦  青砥你太得意忘形了点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  再来一球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱先遣队 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  那个叫立石尚子的 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不是说她很早以前就去世了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是跟男人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是10多年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很恨她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以当我听说她是被男人给骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后变得落魄的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那是她活该
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七惠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然都追到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是你妈妈寄来的信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是她女儿吧  好歹也看下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的信 我要怎样是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这样同意了啊  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样是对死后文的亵渎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对死人表达敬意的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡 我们的工作只是将死后文送达而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后是收信人的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  加油  加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  加油  加油……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 加油……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚去趟医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就让他们开车送你到山下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了就来了 不过也没什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说对不起是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰 虽然这不是我该说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是扔掉了 你也只会比以前更在意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直守在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七惠你真坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:16:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队  队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}五  六
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会想去救人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们送信人是规定不可以做直接跟人类的性命相关的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福音局定下的十四条大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是违反了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  因为文伽很负责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想去确认下死后文是否真的有送到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  是这样的吧  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 想要看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  已经联络过消防队了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  拜托你了老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 老师怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青砥 接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  兰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这个不是道歉就能够弥补的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我这样的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰还是很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的正式比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰到最后都没有气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很出色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一年的比赛中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好的回敬他们了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰从以前就不服输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高中校际比赛的半决赛中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是司线员的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的发球肯定没出界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级的团体赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家输掉的比分全部赢回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊  好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连练习比赛都来看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还一场场都写下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸亏你看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰的妈妈  是一个怎样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视人们各种各样的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,径直奔跑着的你所追求的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了

